## Our aim?

Meaningful meetings between men, whilst having fun with our children. The aim will be to create a ‘village’ feel, and there is space for a couple of camper van/caravans on the edge (let us know if you are bringing one). There will be some communal cooking; although not on the scale of previous years as this campsite doesn’t have kitchen facilities. We will be in touch nearer the time via email to let you know exactly what the catering provision will be. Everyone will be expected to sign up for the rota of cooking, washing up and other jobs on site. 

## What will we do?
Dads are welcome to bring an activity. Dads who have been before will tell you that this is a special feature of the weekend.

