## How many dads?

Max number of Dads is 33. First come first served. We always reserve five spaces for guys who haven’t been before, and for the "Core Group", (currently 7 men) who meet to arrange things before camp. If you are interested in becoming a core group member next year then you will be able to get in touch with any of us at camp - we're looking for new members. 


