## Do you have a friend who wants to come?

At the moment of writing we only have very few space spaces, if you know someone who wants to come you are welcome send them this info but get them to join the waiting list

## How much?
Your contribution of £85 to cover the costs of this year's camp and safeguard the possibility of another great camp in 2023. It does include the cost of the food offered. No-one earns any money from the camp. You can pay what you feel if £85 is a problem. We are not intending to make any profit, but we do want to have £400 surplus from what is sent to us which we expect to use as a 2023 deposit for next years camp. Any surplus left on top of that may be used at the discretion of next year’s core group to be spent on next year's camp. 
